<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="gsz0040b24shiHongChu"><lb
ed="X" n="0040b24"/><anchor n="X.86.1596.0040b24"/><head>第六十九祖衡州南嶽般若寺<persName key="A000241">退翁弘儲</persName>禪師</head><p xml:id="pX86p0040b2401">出通<lb
ed="X" n="0040c01"/>州李氏，帝<persName key="A010090">高陽</persName>之苗裔，虞士師<persName key="A014778">咎繇</persName>後。忼慨重大節，<lb
ed="X" n="0040c02"/>父<persName key="A042781">孝敏先生</persName>，諱<persName key="A042781">嘉兆</persName>，母<persName key="A042484">高</persName>。<ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref>降生前一日，<persName key="A042484">高</persName>夢梵相<lb
ed="X" n="0040c03"/>僧，授金環而生，乳名曰<persName key="A000241">金</persName>。四歲撫于祖母<persName key="A042485">孫</persName>，終日兀<lb
ed="X" n="0040c04"/>坐自語，語不可解，鏘然成文，聽者駭之。<ref type="date" target="#j23095092309862">七歲</ref>聞<ref type="person" target="#A042485">祖母</ref><lb
ed="X" n="0040c05"/>學佛之訓，切憂生死。不樂章句，方外有道之士至，必<lb
ed="X" n="0040c06"/>見，見必深叩，岸然莫當其意。會<persName key="A042483">若昧</persName>法師從匡廬歸，<lb
ed="X" n="0040c07"/>提唱東林<persName key="A001204">遠</persName>法師蓮社遺旨。<ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref>結伴刻漏，修淨業二<lb
ed="X" n="0040c08"/>載，終疑禪宗。慨然曰：「大丈夫一事不知，猶以為恥。況<lb
ed="X" n="0040c09"/><persName key="A002799">如來</persName>大法，不千門萬戶，一躩而開，非夫也。」遂踰城越<lb
ed="X" n="0040c10"/>海，投<persName key="A003668">三峰藏</persName>和尚，剃染圓具，逾年侍<persName key="A003668">藏</persName>。開堂，杭州<persName key="A016073">安<lb
ed="X" n="0040c11"/>隱</persName>師，自期七日明道。至第六日，危立如塑像。堂中開<lb
ed="X" n="0040c12"/>靜，見兩行僧對問訊，嚗然自落積刧未明之事，徹底<lb
ed="X" n="0040c13"/>現前。亟趨方丈，<persName key="A003668">藏</persName>望見顏色曰：「看箭。」<ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref>喝。<persName key="A003668">藏</persName>曰：「看箭。」<lb
ed="X" n="0040c14"/><ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref>又喝。<persName key="A003668">藏</persName>起立大呼曰：「看箭。」<ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref>放身倒。時<persName key="A015874">華嚴鴻</persName>和<lb
ed="X" n="0040c15"/>尚燒香曰：「<persName key="A000241">儲</persName>兄何不禮拜？」<ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref>即下去。<persName key="A003668">藏</persName>當晚小參，<ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref><lb
ed="X" n="0040c16"/>方作禮。<persName key="A003668">藏</persName>問：「萬法歸一，一歸何處？」<ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref>曰：「恰恰今朝，臘<lb
ed="X" n="0040c17"/>月初三。」<persName key="A003668">藏</persName>問：「與<persName key="A004475">趙州</persName>衫子同別？」<ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref>曰：「一滴水一滴凍。」<lb
ed="X" n="0040c18"/><persName key="A003668">藏</persName>問：「如何是奇特事？」適大殿撞鐘。<ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref>曰：「鐘聲咬破七<lb
ed="X" n="0040c19"/>條。」<persName key="A003668">藏</persName>一日上堂，<ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref>……<lb
ed="X" n="0041a02"/>……一僧問同學<lb
ed="X" n="0041a03"/><persName key="A042782">雪生</persName>曰：「紅日出時，<ref type="person" target="#A042782">兄</ref>作麼生？」<persName key="A042782">雪生</persName>請<ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref>代。<ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref>曰：「溪㵎<lb
ed="X" n="0041a04"/>豈能留得住？終歸大海作波濤。」今<persName key="A016082">靈隱禮</persName>和尚適城<lb
ed="X" n="0041a05"/>中回，<persName key="A042782">雪生</persName>理前問，<persName key="A016082">禮</persName>答亦如是。<ref type="person" target="#A003668">老和尚</ref>聞之，擊案賞<lb
ed="X" n="0041a06"/>曰：「二子當起吾宗。」<ref type="person" target="#A000241">師</ref>服勤又三年，益臻玄奧，<persName key="A003668">藏</persName>乃書<lb
ed="X" n="0041a07"/>臨濟正宗記付之。……<lb
ed="X" n="0041a10"/>……由天封、慧明，深入東掖山跡，三年不出。為天台<lb
ed="X" n="0041a11"/><persName key="A042783">文<roleName>邑侯</roleName>可紀</persName>，請住國清。……</p>
